## ðŸŽ¯ Best Practices

### Do:
- Always include dark mode variants
- Use theme colors from [src/config/theme.js](mdc:src/config/theme.js)
- Test both light and dark modes
- Use consistent color combinations
- Leverage the centralized theme system

### Don't:
- Hardcode colors (use theme colors)
- Forget dark mode variants
- Mix different color systems
- Use too many colors (stick to primary, secondary, accent)

